        "text_block_cwmrAL": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Best UPF Protection",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Created for women who spend long days in the sun, this collection features our most protective swimwear designs. While all Ocean Soul fabrics are UPF-rated, these styles offer enhanced coverage and darker colourways for added sun protection.</p><p>From long sleeve swimsuits to supportive one pieces and rash guards, each piece is thoughtfully designed to stay on, flatter your shape, and move with you in and out of the water.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_DMFYyV": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Our most loved style, the Sulawesi long sleeve one piece, is a customer favourite for good reason. It’s a high-performance one piece swimsuit made to stay in place through duck dives, surf sessions, and ocean swims – yet looks sleek and stylish poolside or on the sand. Whether you’re an athlete, a mum chasing little ones at the beach, or someone who just wants extra sun coverage without sacrificing style, the Sulawesi was made with you in mind.</p><p></p><p></p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_384xVz": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Unlike standard swimsuits that stretch, fade, or lose shape after one season, Ocean Soul long sleeve swimsuits are designed to last twice as long. Every piece is ethically made in Bali, combining form, function, and sustainability – for women who expect more from their swimwear.  From the lineup to the lounge chair, these are long sleeve swimsuits you’ll actually feel good in – and good about.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
      },
