        "caption_horizontal": 50,
        "heading": "",
        "subheading_text": "<p>Unlike standard suits that stretch, fade, or lose shape after one season, Ocean Soul long sleeve swimsuits are designed to last twice as long. Every piece is ethically made in Bali, combining form, function, and sustainability – for women who expect more from their swimwear.</p><p>Panelled design that cinches the waist and flatters your figure</p><p>Double lining for support – no padding needed<br/></p><p>Premium YKK zipper that stays put and won’t rust<br/></p><p>High neckline and long sleeves for extra sun protection<br/></p><p>Minimalist block colours for a timeless, slimming effect<br/></p><p>This is a long sleeve swimsuit that works just as hard as you do – and makes you feel incredible doing it.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
