    "image_with_text_gHycEF": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/white-navy-long-sleeve-one-piece-swimsuit-the-sulawesi-ocean-soul-swimwear-4.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "UPF 50+ Sun Protection Built In",
        "text": "<p>When you're out on the water for hours, sun protection isn’t optional – it’s essential. Our long sleeve one piece swimsuits offer UPF 50+ coverage, shielding your skin from harmful UV rays while reducing your need for chemical sunscreen. That means safer skin and cleaner oceans – all in one beautifully designed swimsuit.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_9VtixN": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/long-sleeve-swimsuit-the-sulawesi-in-snow-ocean-soul-swimwear-11.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Designed to Sculpt, Stay On, and Feel Amazing",
        "text": "<p>Let’s face it: most long sleeve swimsuits either feel too sporty or not secure enough for real movement. The Sulawesi, our best-selling long sleeve one piece swimsuit, bridges the gap – offering high performance support with a sleek, feminine cut that enhances your shape without restricting movement.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_3PxM3A": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/long-sleeve-swimsuit-the-sulawesi-snow-and-navy-ocean-soul-swimwear-14.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Made from Sustainable Italian Fabric",
        "text": "<p>Crafted from recycled ECONYL® yarn, each piece diverts ocean waste like discarded fishing nets and repurposes it into premium performance swimwear. Our eco-conscious fabric feels incredibly soft against your skin yet holds firm through surf, salt, and repeated wear.</p><p>Ocean Soul long sleeve swimsuits are built to last twice as long as regular swimwear, helping you buy less, wear longer, and support a more sustainable future.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
