        "text_align": "center",
        "caption_vertical": 0,
        "caption_horizontal": 0,
        "heading": "Built for water women",
        "subheading_text": "<p></p><p></p><p><strong>Whether you’re surfing, swimming laps or beach walking with your kids, our suits are designed to stay on and hold their shape. No riding up, no gaping, no fuss – just secure, all-day wear you<br/>don’t have to think twice about.  Trusted by active women around the world.</strong></p><p><strong>That’s why Ocean Soul Swimwear is trusted by active women around the world, from surfers in Australia to freedivers in Tahiti to eco-minded travellers looking for functional fashion they can count on.</strong></p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
